# LogDriftScope - Log Shift and Pattern Monitor

LogDriftScope identifies subtle but dangerous shifts in log behavior by tracking burst patterns and keyword surges.

## Features
- Drift and burst detection  
- Frequency windowing  
- CLI-friendly timeline scan  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/main_LogDriftScope.git
cd main_LogDriftScope
python analyze.py
